  23 Jul 2004; Tom Gall <tgall@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  stable on ppc64

  17 Jul 2004; Armando Di Cianno <fafhrd@gentoo.org>
  hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  Added ~ARCH for ppc64. (bug #57036)

  01 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  virtual/glibc -> virtual/libc

  26 Apr 2004; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  Added gnuconfig_update for hppa. Marked ~hppa.

  20 Mar 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  RDEPEND fix for bug #44816.

  18 Mar 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  inherit eutils for epatch

  16 Mar 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  doesn't need to RDEPEND on anything (in response to bug #44817)

  19 Feb 2004; Brad House <brad_mssw@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild,
  files/hermes-1.3.2-amd64.patch:
  patch for amd64. GCC would ICE because of bad casting. The rest of this
  package probably needs to be cleaned up too

  29 Sep 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha

*hermes-1.3.2-r2 (14 Apr 2002)

  19 Jun 2003; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild:
  Added ~mips to KEYWORDS

  10 Feb 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild :
  Add ~alpha to KEYWORDS.  Fixup gnuconfig to recognize alpha arches.

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords

  14 Apr 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> all files
  This selection was moved to media-libs from app-games, since it is not
  a game, but a game/graphics library for use by games.  Artem from
  the previous ChangeLog entry brought this to my attention.

  14 Apr 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild
  New revision to fix autogen errors.  The fix was submitted in bug #1720
  by artm@nerve.v2.nl (Artem Baguinski)

